abstract: >-
  HARSAT is for the assessment of data
  concerning contaminants (hazardous substances) and their
  effects in the marine environment. The code includes tools
  for pre-processing data, statistical trend analysis and
  comparison with threshold values, and post-processing for
  archiving and reporting.
